    <h3>Update 1.1.0: Notes and Backend</h3>
    <h4>1/10/2023</h4>
    <p>Today's update configures some things for me on the back end, but more importantly gives us a notes button on each creature in the Encounter Table.
        Want to track who's fighting who? Want to note if a creature has a reaction of some kind? Want to go back and check a creature's saving throw modifier
